Dont be fooled. NYPD and the Government is the biggest gang out there. Rather than giving us a pit, they spend their time exactly like this making a high production video for their instagram to show “the people” that they are doing everything they can to stop ATV’s, Cars, Drifting and Speeding 😭😂🤡 Guessing how we can solve this? GIVE US A PIT AND A PLACE FOR US TO RIDE THATS NOT 4 HOURS AWAY. Heres the crazy part. We bought land upstate near absolutely NO ONE and started to build a pit and NY officials shut it down. We spent over a year trying to buy warehouse’s, getting permits for parks, renting out stadium lots, literally everything you can think of in NY & NJ!!! The government makes it impossible for us to rent out a place so we can do these things. Instead what they will do is tell “the people” that they are doing everything they can to stop “this” meanwhile denying every possible legal way of doing it so the government makes money 🤡We will be at an intersection in the industrials bothering no one, but cops will come to chase us out and follow us the whole night for us to go on public streets to create more havic to cause accidents, give tickets, and take cars ALL FOR THE MONEY!!!! WeAreInTheMovie is about to do its biggest transition for the better and we hope you guys will continue to be apart of the journey. We first want to say thank you to all of our supporters not only from New York but from everywhere around the world. For the past two years the support has ben unreal. Dreams finally became true and we now have a spot to throw LEGAL PIT EVENTS 🎉 From time to time (on big holidays) we may slip in a takeover but overall we have a new agenda. We want to throw legal pit events in NY / and all around the United States. We also want to start drifting at other peoples takeovers / events with the WeAreInTheMovie Drift Team, film for youtube and make our underground shop’s and businesses open to the public that which as well brings in a lot of job opportunities. We are not leaving the scene and want to make that clear! Its a blessing to be in the position we are in now and its all thanks to you guys. The person that started this brand, his passion is not really just cars. Its mainly throwing events and building brands. For 10 years he was throwing the biggest concerts in America and then he had to stop because of the “pandemic”. Thats how Imthat335/WeAreInTheMovie started. We just love getting a bunch of people together to create memories that people will remember for the rest of their lives! We will be throwing our last takeover this weekend before our first LEGAL EVENT THATS SOON TO BE ANNOUNCED 🎉 Wait for the flyer to drop this Friday for the takeover. 

Subscribers that stay subscribed for over 6 months will get perks at our legal pit events! Discounts on food/drinks and will also get free admission! We have multiple dates set for multiple events already at this one location. We plan on building a stadium and finding multiple locations in the future for New York that is super local. That is the goal and we will not stop until its done. We are working very hard behind the scenes to make sure the first Legal pit event in New York is something you have never seen before! 

Drop a “❤️” down below if we have your support.

~WeAreInTheMovie

Come celebrate WeAreInTheMovie’s last takeover with his day ones 💯 We had to make sure this was a special one. The time of the takeover will be on the location list. NGL teared up a couple times but we know we on to bigger and better things and its only for you guys ⭐️ 

Anyone thats confused on why this is our last takeover, you can take a look at our most recent post. We are very excited to show you guys and announce our New York legal pit after this and for sure hope to see everyone there. It for sure will be the biggest legal pit event in America from the biggest names in the takeover scene to people coming from all around the United States 🇺🇸🫡

Love every one of you guys and appreciate all the support everyone has given us for the past two years! Time to close a chapter and open up another one 📗❤️

~ WeAreInTheMovie ⭐️
